The paper deals with recommender systems and modeling user behavior in review communities. The most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with recommendation systems. The paper also uses latent models and machine learning techniques, which are common in categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with natural language processing and writing style, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper deals with temporal evolution, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
